Diamond Home Services files stock offer . Diamond Home Services Inc said it had filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission for an offering of 750 , 000 shares . In a statement issued August 28 , Diamond Home said all of the shares are being offered by a shareholder , Globe Building Materials Inc . There will be no underwriter over - allotment option . William Blair & Co will manage the underwriting group for the offering . - - Chicago Newsdesk 312 - 408 - 8787 
